ews/09/22/nuggets.trade.ap/index.html|archivedate=April 16, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Retired numbers===\n{{retired number list|<ref name=\"cbs_houston\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/nba/teams/history/HOU|title=Houston Rockets|date=May 15, 2010|accessdate=May 15, 2010|work=CBS Sports|publisher=CBS Interactive}}</ref>\n{{retired number|image=Retiredyao1.jpg|alt=25|name=[[Yao Ming|Yao<br />Ming]]|pos=C<br />&nbsp;|date=February 3, 2017}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredDrexler1.jpg|alt=25|name=[[Clyde Drexler|Clyde<br />Drexler]]|pos=G<br />&nbsp;|date=February 3, 2000}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredMurphy1.jpg|alt=7|name=[[Calvin Murphy|Calvin<br />Murphy]]|pos=G<br />&nbsp;|date=March 17, 1984}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredMalone1.jpg|alt=24|name=[[Moses Malone|Moses<br />Malone]]|pos=C<br />&nbsp;|date=April 19, 1998}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredOlajuwon1.jpg|alt=32|name=[[Hakeem Olajuwon|Hakeem<br />Olajuwon]]|pos=C<br />&nbsp;|date=November 9, 2002}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredTomjanovich1.jpg|alt=5|name=[[Rudy Tomjanovich|Rudy<br />Tomjanovich]]<sup>1</sup>|pos=F<br />&nbsp;|date=January 28, 1982}}\n{{retired number|image=RetiredDawson1.jpg|alt=32|name=[[Carroll Dawson|Carroll<br />Dawson]]<sup>2</sup>||pos=Assistant coach<br />General manager|honored=April 16, 2007}}\n}}\n* <sup>1</sup> ''Also served as head coach (1991\u20132003).''\n* <sup>2</sup> ''As Dawson did not play for the Rockets, the team used his initials.''<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/Rockets_will_honor_general_man-218952-34.html |title=Tribute to Dawson |last=Pierce |first=Damien |date=April 4, 2007 |publisher=NBA.com |accessdate=February 24, 2009}}</ref>\n\n===Basketball Hall of Famers===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"5\" style=\"{{NBA color cell|Houston Rockets}};\"|Houston Rockets Hall of Famers<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hoophall.com/hall-of-famers-index/|title=Hall of Famers|accessdate=February 14, 2015